{"tid":2227041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【加速主義】意甲高列巴尼IG要求釋放維吾爾族人 小粉紅心碎：你呢隻猩猩斷腳啦","createTime":"2020-10-02T12:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T12:52:08.000Z","uid":2054,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95c42b34a2e6c6e0407a3495d7823e1db3622c51","tid":2227041,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201001/LUYQP2YS4RB6ZFLVV6JTINCVSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201001%2FLUYQP2YS4RB6ZFLVV6JTINCVSY%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=3f552055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201001%2FLUYQP2YS4RB6ZFLVV6JTINCVSY%2F&h=ee2e6540\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201001/LUYQP2YS4RB6ZFLVV6JTINCVSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7emI3WDHeeAlVpvPeTfjFTW1Y94=/364x96/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2ULYXL3DRFECJENA5F7RNIAAGQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7emI3WDHeeAlVpvPeTfjFTW1Y94%3D%2F364x96%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2ULYXL3DRFECJENA5F7RNIAAGQ.png&h=a0e7ee37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有中國網民稱高列巴尼為「猩猩」<br />\n<br />\n中共多年來打壓迫害百萬名新疆維吾爾族人，惡名傳遍國際，此前曾經因為在Twitter發表批評中國政府打壓維吾爾族人言論的奧斯爾，被中國傳媒進行封殺，至今在大陸的任何報道也無法再看到奧斯爾這個名字，改以「10號」代替。周四拿玻里後衞高列巴尼就在IG發文，聲援被拘留在新疆集中營的維吾爾族人，不過此舉又令到中國網民隨即在高列巴尼的IG下留言，更有人侮辱這位拿玻里後衞為「猩猩」。<br />\n<br />\n中共被指在新疆建立集中營迫害維吾爾族人，此前一直有不少體育球星聲援維吾爾族人，這次輪到高列巴尼在IG上發聲：「上百萬維吾爾族穆斯林在新疆集中營被拘留以及遭受酷刑。不是因為他們做了什麼錯事，只是因為他們的種族。這是21世紀最大規模的監禁，這個情況必須結束。」"},{"pid":"a22a1fb21eba2b073a42b70fcb6c80db173882e5","tid":2227041,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"仲有列貝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b82415515d0001f3564b46088dee109df37985","tid":2227041,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940e18fbf812bbae2ee951089b2e0409c65fa310","tid":2227041,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a22a1fb21eba2b073a42b70fcb6c80db173882e5","tid":2227041,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"仲有列貝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"朱元璋後人"},{"pid":"d7162bb7c0112dc1d89c8f0adf0dfdf037cdd45f","tid":2227041,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"世一中堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a380c7570b4f599a39a6521fd20569f97b61dbb","tid":2227041,"uid":117689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"點解班on9咁鍾意去人地地頭打中文<br />\n或者留埋d乜春NMSL<br />\n人地撚睇得明你UP乜"}]}